title: [Week 13] LP Forest Rewards
body:
What should be done for Week 13 of LP Forest rewards?

Do nothing - keep current setup (3T/week to 9 LP Forests total)

Double rewards for KuSwap LPs to 1T/week each for 3 LPs (4.5T/week for 9 LP Forests total)

Double rewards for KoffeeSwap LPs to 500B/week each for 3 LPs (3.75T/week for 9 LP Forests total)

Double rewards for Shibance LPs to 500B/week each for 3 LPs (3.75T/week for 9 LP Forests total)
